<li><a href="http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/equal-opportunity/" class="external text" title="http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/equal-opportunity/" rel="nofollow">Equality of opportunity</a>, by R. Arneson (2002).</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www.columbia.edu/cu/cup/catalog/data/023108/0231081200.HTM" class="external text" title="http://www.columbia.edu/cu/cup/catalog/data/023108/0231081200.HTM" rel="nofollow">Lepowsky, Maria. 1993. <i>Fruit of the Motherland: Gender in an Egalitarian Society.</i> New York: Columbia University Press.</a></li>
